118
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:49,584
Judy! Yo, Judy!
How you doin'?

119
00:11:50,251 --> 00:11:51,252
Alright.

120
00:11:51,461 --> 00:11:53,254
Who's the wimp?

121
00:11:53,838 --> 00:11:55,256
Oh, that's Ricky.

122
00:11:55,465 --> 00:11:57,175
Wasn't he the kid you were
babysitting last year?

123
00:11:57,383 --> 00:11:59,469
Guess I'm not good
enough for her anymore.

124
00:12:05,683 --> 00:12:07,018
Well, here you go, Angela.

125
00:12:07,226 --> 00:12:09,103
If you need anything,
I'll be in bunk 19, below.

126
00:12:09,312 --> 00:12:10,271
Second from the bottom.

127
00:12:17,779 --> 00:12:20,365
- Who were those guys?
