00:18:48,336 --> 00:18:50,129
Now get the hell over
here and help me down.

210
00:18:52,340 --> 00:18:53,132
Come on, kid.

211
00:18:54,008 --> 00:18:56,886
Get me down and I'll make you
a nice ice cream sundae, okay?

212
00:18:59,889 --> 00:19:01,724
Hey, what the--
